<div class=Section1>

<h1><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                                                                                                                                                          
</span></h1>

<h1>Why use patterns?</h1>

<p class=MsoNormal><i>Patterns help you learn from other’s successes, instead
of your own failures</i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b>Mark Johnson </b>(cited by B. <span
class=SpellE>Eckel</span>)</p>

<h3>An additional layer of abstraction</h3>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><i>separate
     things that change from things that stay the same</i></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'>distilling
     out common factors between a family of similar problems</li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'>similar
     to design</li>
</ul>

<h3>Insightful and clever way to solve a particular <i>class of problems<o:p></o:p></i></h3>

<ul style='margin-top:0in' type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list .5in'>most
     general and flexible solution</li>
</ul>

<h3>Algorithmic form of patterns</h3>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'>IF<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>you find yourself in CONTEXT</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    
</span><span class=GramE>for</span> example EXAMPLES,</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    
</span><span class=GramE>with</span> PROBLEM,</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    
</span><span class=GramE>entailing</span> FORCES</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'>THEN for some REASONS,</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    
</span><span class=GramE>apply</span> DESIGN FORM AND/OR RULE</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    
</span><span class=GramE>to</span> construct SOLUTION</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    
</span><span class=GramE>leading</span> to NEW CONTEXT and </p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                </span>OTHER
PATTERNS</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

</div>

